comment: * Indicates the errors that are applicable only to the streaming use-case

variables.name: ERROR_CONCURRENT_SERVICE_LIMIT_REACHED
variables.comment: Indicates that the middleware cannot start a stream due to too many ongoing streams

variables.name: ERROR_UNABLE_TO_START_SERVICE
variables.comment: Indicates that the middleware was unable to start the streaming service

variables.name: ERROR_DUPLICATE_START_STREAM
variables.comment:
* Indicates that the app called
         * {@link MbmsStreamingSession#startStreaming(StreamingServiceInfo,
         * java.util.concurrent.Executor, StreamingServiceCallback)}
         * more than once for the same {@link StreamingServiceInfo}.
